org.gvsig.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.symbols

Interface IMultiLayerSymbol

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, IPrintable, ISymbol, Persistent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMultiChartSymbol, IMultiLayerFillSymbol, IMultiLayerLineSymbol, IMultiLayerMarkerSymbol
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiLayerFillSymbol, MultiLayerLineSymbol, MultiLayerMarkerSymbol

    public interface IMultiLayerSymbol
extends ISymbol
    Allows to create multi layer symbols using the composition of several symbols of the same type.Depending on the type of the symbols that are used to compose the final symbol, the user will have MultiLayerMarkerSymbol, MultiLayerLineSymbol,...
